Package finalProject

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RunnerConstants
    The RunnerConstants interface represents constants for application of the Runner class.
    RunnerDAO
    The RunnerDAO interface inherits functionality of RunnerConstants, RunnerReader and RunnerWriter interfaces
    RunnerReader
    The RunnerReader interface represents input functionality of data sources for applications of the Runner class.
    RunnerWriter
    The RunnerWriter interface represents output functionality of data sources for applications of the Runner class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAOFactory
    The DAOFactory class provides selection from various data sources (including Text file, XML file, Derby database, hard-coded Default)
    Runner
    The Runner class represents a runner in a race.
    RunnerApp
    The RunnerApp class represents a race between multiple competitors with indeterminate outcome.
    RunnerDB
    The RunnerDB class implements the RunnerDAO interface with Derby database as data source.
    RunnerDefault
    The RunnerText class implements the RunnerDAO interface with default data hard-coded.
    RunnerText
    The RunnerText class implements the RunnerDAO interface with text file as data source.
    RunnerXML
    The RunnerXML class implements the RunnerDAO interface with XML file as data source.
    StringUtils
    The StringUtils class provides utility methods for manipulating strings.
    ThreadRunner
    The ThreadRunner class inherits functionality from Runner, and provides execution in threads.
    Validator
    The Validator class provides utility methods to prompt for user input and validate responses.
